<h3>Complexity Analysis<span class="absolute -mt-20" id="complexity-analysis"></span>
    <a href="#complexity-analysis" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"></a></h3><ul>
<li><strong>Time Complexity</strong>: The time complexity of the DFS algorithm is O(V + E), where V is the number of vertices and E is the number of edges in the graph.</li>
<li><strong>Space Complexity</strong>: The space complexity of the DFS algorithm is O(V), where V is the number of vertices in the graph.</li>
</ul>
